**Technical Skills:**
- Deep knowledge of manufacturing IT/OT (ERP, MES, SCADA, PLCs, IoT)
- Cloud architecture (Azure expertise)
- Data architecture (data lakes, analytics, AI/ML)
- Integration patterns (APIs, events, messaging)
